name: ELEX WooCommerce Australia Post Shipping
author: ELEXtensions

sections.description:
ELEX WooCommerce Australia Post Shipping plugin automates your shipping process by fetching the shipping rates ( Domestic & International ) using Australia Post APIs. Based on the shipping destination location and properties of the items added to the cart, eligible Australia Post services will be fetched & displayed on the Cart and Checkout page. Customers can choose the desired service and proceed with the checkout.

Integrates WooCommerce to Australia Post

Once ELEX WooCommerce Australia Post Shipping plugin is installed and configured with the necessary information (please visit the installation section for more info), your WordPress/WooCommerce Shop will be ready to ship using Australia Post. This plugin will add the Australia Post shipping method as one of the shipping methods in WooCommerce. The Basic plugin works for both contracted and non-contracted accounts.

Top Features

  • Access Australia Post Real-time Rates
  • Choose AusPost non-contracted account or eParcel contracted account
  • Show cheapest rates to Customers
  • Combined Export
  • Offer Australia Post services to only specific countries

Australia Post Services

Plugin Supports both Domestic and International DHL Express Services. Few of those services are listed below.
* EXPRESS NATIONAL FULL RATE
* NATIONAL FULL RATE
* INTL ECONOMY W SOD/ REGD POST
* INTL STANDARD/PACK & TRACK
* INTL EXPRESS MERCH/ECI MERCH
* INTL ECONOMY/AIRMAIL PARCELS
* PARCEL POST + SIGNATURE
* EXPRESS POST + SIGNATURE

Premium version – Real-time Rates and Label Printing

ELEX WooCommerce Australia Post Shipping – Premium Version Features

  • Print Shipping Label with Postage.
  • Supports Australia Post eParcel and Australia Post StarTrack Service.
  • Australia Post MyPost – Rates & Print Shipping Labels powerd by ReachShip Multi-Carrier Shipping Platform
  • Estimated Delivery Date.
  • Print eParcel Shipping Label (for Contracted Rates).
  • eParcel International Shipping Documents.
  • Australia Post Order Summary / Manifest.
  • Box packing – Pack the items in the cart to configured boxes.
  • Weight-Based Packing.
  • Price Adjustment for Each Shipping Service.
  • Customization Option for Each Service Name.
  • Service Level Signature/Registered Options.
  • Service Level Extra Cover Charges.
  • Australia Post Shipment Tracking.
  • Timely compatibility updates and bug fixes.
  • Premium support!

Upgrade to Premium!

About ELEXtensions

We are a group of WordPress and WooCommerce enthusiasts with a vision to solve genuine problems related to WordPress & WooCommerce stores.

About Australia Post

Australia Post, formally the Australian Postal Corporation, is the government business enterprise that provides postal services in Australia. It operates in three core areas: letters and associated services; retail merchandise and agency services; and parcels and logistics. Australia Post operates regular mail delivery as well as an express/courier service through Messenger Post (Now trading as Startrack Courier). Australia post also has an optional service called MyPost where you can create an account and manage your delivery.
sections.installation:
1. Upload the plugin folder to the /wp-content/plugins/ directory.
  2. Activate the plugin through the Plugins menu in WordPress.
  3. Thats it! you can now configure the plugin.
sections.faq:
Is the plugin configuration complicated?

The plugin is very easy to configure. The documentation includes a step-by-step tutorial, FAQs, Troubleshooting Guide, Knowledge Base and Code snippets.
